\p
\v 1 The following events happened during the reign¦228506 of \add King\add* Ahasuerus¦228503.\x + \xo 1:1: \xt Ezr 4:6.\x* (\add Also known as King Xerxes,\add* he ruled \add the empire of Persia\add* with 127 provinces¦228514 from India¦228507 all the way across to Ethiopia¦228510.)
