\p
\v 3 In the third year of his reign¦228531, he hosted a celebration for all of his officials and for every important person who worked for him, as well as the officers who served in the army of the \add combined empire\add* of Persia¦228540 and Media¦228541, the wealthy landowners, and the officials of the provinces¦228544. The king was present¦228545 in person \add to host the celebration\add*
\v 4 which, over a period of six months, would display¦228547 the incredible wealth and prestige of his empire and his personal wealth and power.
