\v 8 and¦228646 it was served according¦228628 to his rule: There¦228631 is no compulsion to drink¦228627, but all of his servants were to give each guest however much they wanted.
\p
\v 9 Meanwhile, Queen Vashti¦228649 was hosting a celebration for the women¦228653 \add in a different part\add* of the king's royal¦228655 palace.
