\p
\v 16 Then Memukan answered the king, \add speaking loudly enough that\add* both the king and his officials could hear. “Queen Vashti¦228794 has done wrong,” he said, “and not only against the king. She has also done wrong against all the officials and people¦228806 groups in all the provinces¦228810 that King Ahasuerus¦228812 \add rules\add*!
