\p
\v 1 Some time later when King Ahasuerus¦228964 no longer felt so angry, he \add started to miss\add* Vashti¦228968. But when she'd disobeyed his command, he had made a decree \add that she could never come into his presence again¦228977\add*.
\v 2 So¦228979 some of the young men who served the king suggested to him, “\add Your majesty, you should¦228984 get a new wife for yourself.\add* You could tell your servants to look for young virgins¦228987 who are very beautiful.
\v 3 You could assign officers in each province¦228996 of your empire to bring every¦229001 virgin who is very beautiful here to your capital city of Shushan¦229010. They could stay in the harem for virgins under the custody of Hegai¦229019, the castrated royal guardian who takes care of the young women who live there and he could arrange for them to receive beauty treatments¦229025.
\v 4 Then¦229027 you could decide which young¦229027 woman¦229027 you like best and then make her queen instead of Vashti¦229034.”
