\p
\v 1 Three days later, the \add Queen\add* Esther¦230232 put on her royal robes¦230231 and \add went and\add* stood¦230234 in the inner¦230239 courtyard¦230235 of the palace, across from the king's house. He was in the royal palace, sitting¦230244 on the royal throne¦230247 and facing the room's entrance¦230252.
