\p
\v 1 That same day¦231099, King Ahasuerus¦231103 gave Queen Esther all the property that had belonged to Haman¦231109, the enemy of the Jews. Esther told the king that Mordekai was \add her cousin and that he had been like a father\add* to her, and \add so the king summoned\add* Mordekai to come to him.
